OL,3,CDisneyland workers approve first
OL,4,Cstrike in 40 years
OL,6,FIt is often described as the "happiest
OL,7,Fplace on Earth", but more than a few
OL,8,Fworkers at Southern California's
OL,9,FDisneyland Park have cause to be upset.
OL,11,FMany are struggling to cover rent and
OL,12,Fother basic expenses with their pay,
OL,13,Fwith some even resorting to living in
OL,14,Ftheir cars despite having second and
OL,15,Fthird jobs.
