OL,3,CDisneyland workers approve first
OL,4,Cstrike in 40 years
OL,6,FA group of four unions representing
OL,7,F14,000 Disneyland Resort employees in
OL,8,FCalifornia have been negotiating for
OL,9,Fbetter pay and working conditions
OL,10,Fsince April, but as talks stalled,
OL,11,Fworkers on Friday voted overwhelmingly
OL,12,Fto authorise a potential strike.
OL,14,FNow that the vote has passed, it's up
OL,15,Fto union leadership to decide whether
OL,16,Fto hold one. It would be the first at
OL,17,FDisney's original resort in 40 years.
