OL,6,FUnion leaders said if the strike
OL,7,Fhappens, it would likely be of a
OL,8,Flimited duration, unlike the open-
OL,9,Fended strikes by actors' and writers'
OL,10,Funions in 2023.
OL,12,FThis potential strike, approved by 99%
OL,13,Fof those who voted, would officially
OL,14,Fbe about Disney not allowing union
OL,15,Fbuttons to be worn at work.
