OL,6,FThe SEIU-USWW, Teamsters Local 495,
OL,7,FUCFW Local 324 and BCTGM Local 83
OL,8,Funions all filed charges with the
OL,9,FNational Labor Relations Board against
OL,10,FDisney in June for what they said were
OL,11,Fhundreds of instances of unlawful
OL,12,Fdiscipline, intimidation and
OL,13,Fsurveillance of union members wearing
OL,14,Fthese buttons at work.
OL,16,FHowever, the underlying concern among
OL,17,Frank-and-file workers is about the
OL,18,Fcurrent contract that many say does
OL,19,Fnot provide a liveable wage.
