OL,6,FVoters in the city of Anaheim in
OL,7,FOrange County, CA, where the
OL,8,FDisneyland Resort is located, had
OL,9,Fpreviously approved a measure that
OL,10,Frequired the resort's employees to
OL,11,Fmake a $19.90 minimum wage as of
OL,12,FJanuary of 2024.
OL,14,FBut in a county where the 2022 median
OL,15,Frent was $2,251 a month, and where
OL,16,Fabout 10% of residents live in
OL,17,Fpoverty, workers said a wage of about
OL,18,F$20 an hour is still not enough.
