OL,6,FAnother 4,500 employees in the same
OL,7,Fbargaining group work at the Downtown
OL,8,FDisney retail and dining district, the
OL,9,FDisney hotels, or the resort's other
OL,10,Ftheme park, Disney California
OL,11,FAdventure. Their contract expires in
OL,12,FSeptember, and they are not part of
OL,13,Fthe current strike developments.
OL,15,FTogether, they represent about 40% of
OL,16,Fthe entire resort's employees. But
OL,17,Fonly the Disneyland Park employees
OL,18,Fwill vote and participate in a strike
OL,19,Ffor now. The unions and Disneyland
OL,20,Fhave two more meetings scheduled for
OL,21,Fon Monday and Tuesday.
