OL,6,FDisneyland officials said the wearing
OL,7,Fof union buttons goes against the
OL,8,Fparks' uniform policy and that only a
OL,9,F"handful" of employees have been
OL,10,Fdisciplined.
OL,12,FIn a statement, officials said the
OL,13,Fparks strive to give guests "an
OL,14,Funinterrupted, immersive experience,"
OL,15,Fand that "anything that distracts from
